name: Return of the War God
author: Myosu &#40묘수&#41
content: The worst talent that no one can compete with. Unstoppable Demon God, Dan Uhyeon.A thousand years after being sealed for the misdeed. A thousand years was enough to get rid of Dan Uhyeon&#039s sense of superiority. A world that has changed, solitude with no one knows, and the only thing left is despondency and emptiness.&quotTime goes like the wind.
